title: 7 AM HOUR - The Biggest Suck Up on the Show...
description: It's a cold Monday but we're here to help you through it!  We discuss the crime in downtown Minneapolis, we have a special guest in to host Think Fast, Weekend X Factor, we talk to a private investigator to see what people hire him for and what kind of crazy stories he has, it's Boss's Day! so the boss Rich is on to quiz us on who knows him best!
